.el .IP "replaceData($offset, \f(CW$length\fR, \f(CW$string\fR)" 4
.IX Item "replaceData($offset, $length, $string)"
.Vb 1
\&  $text\->replaceData($offset, $length, $string);
.Ve
.Sp
The DOM style version to replace node data.
